uire-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Liam-Gallagher-and-John-Squire-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Liam-Gallagher-and-John-Squire-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Liam-Gallagher-and-John-Squire-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Liam-Gallagher-and-John-Squire-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Liam-Gallagher-and-John-Squire-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-squire">约翰·斯奎尔 (John Squire)</a>通过视频和官方网站进一步预告了他们的合作专辑。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/liam-gallagher-oasis-reunion-tour-noel-interview-2020-new-album-2615869"><em>NME</em>大读物 – Liam Gallagher：“绿洲团聚很快就会发生”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位前<a href="/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>歌手去年 6 月首次透露了两人合作的想法，当时他邀请这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stone-roses">The Stone Roses</a>吉他手在他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/liam-gallagher-live-in-knebworth-kasabian-amyl-sniffers-3239799">Knebworth 演出</a>中演奏 1995 年 Oasis 经典歌曲“Champagne Supernova”。 “超级团队即将到来 LG JS，”加拉格尔当时的一条推文中写道。</p><p>去年 9 月，加拉格尔<a href="https://music.apple.com/us/curator/matt-wilkinson/1184566442?app=music&amp;ls=1&amp;ct=cur_am1_mattwilkinson_gen&amp;itscg=80170&amp;itsct=cur_am1_mattwilkinson_gen">在 Apple Music 1 上接受马特·威尔金森 (Matt Wilkinson)</a>采访时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-confirms-he-and-the-stone-roses-john-squire-are-in-supergroup-talks-3314922">证实，两人“肯定”会合作</a>。在回应威尔金森更新最新情况的请求时，加拉格尔说：“是的。严肃的人。但我们首先有事情要做，他也有事情要清理等等。但是，是的，我肯定会在某个时候做总结。”</p><p>早在十月，加拉格尔就在他的 X/Twitter 帐户上调侃说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-teases-joint-album-with-john-squire-as-the-best-record-since-the-beatles-revolver-3520505">两人的联合 LP 将是“自《Revolver》以来最好的唱片”</a> ，并声称这张专辑将比<a href="/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>的第七张 LP 更好。</p><p>另一位歌迷对加拉格尔的推文做出了回应，称其为“重大声明”，而这位歌手则回复道：“即将到来的事情会更大，我很谦虚，它到处都是。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C1AIoBeomvZ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 